---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const pageTitle = "Corey Stewart Resumes";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <h1 class="pt-8 pb-8 text-center text-3xl">Resumes</h1>
    <div
        class="flex flex-col justify-around items-center sm:flex-row sm:justify-around px-4 sm:px-0"
    >
        <!-- Tech Resume -->
        <a href="/CoreyStewartTech.pdf" download>
            <div class="text-center">
                <h2 class="text-2xl inline-block pb-2">
                    Technical Resume <br />
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div
                class="inline-block transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform origin-top-center hover:scale-110 m-2"
            >
                <img src="/images/resumeTech.png" class="h-80 mx-auto filter contrast-75" />
            </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/CoreyStewartTalent.pdf" download>
            <h2 class="text-2xl text-center pb-2">
                Talent Resume<br />
            </h2>
            <div
                class="inline-block transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform origin-top-center hover:scale-110 m-2"
            >
                <img src="/images/resumeTalent.png" class="h-80 mx-auto filter contrast-75" />
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
    <p class="pt-12 italic">
        "A human being should be able to change a diaper, plan an invasion,
        butcher a hog, conn a ship, design a building, write a sonnet, balance
        accounts, build a wall, set a bone, comfort the dying, take orders, give
        orders, cooperate, act alone, solve equations, analyze a new problem,
        pitch manure, program a computer, cook a tasty meal, fight efficiently,
        die gallantly. Specialization is for insects." â€“ Robert A. Heinlein
    </p>
</BaseLayout>
